they%20will%20be%20unable%20to%20engage%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20block%20can%20be%20used%20by%20users%20to%20share%20and%20hide%20harmful%20or%20private%20information%20about%20those%20they've%20blocked.%20Users%20will%20be%20able%20to%20see%20if%20such%20behavior%20occurs%20with%20this%20update%2C%20allowing%20for%20greater%20transparency%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20X%20engineering%20team%20said%20in%20a%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20the%20change%20say%20it%20could%20make%20X%20less%20safe%20for%20some%20users%2C%20such%20as%20victims%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flos-angeles-basic-income-program-domestic-violence-survivors-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edomestic%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EX%20did%20not%20provide%20comment%20on%20these%20concerns%20when%20reached%20by%20BI%2C%20instead%20referring%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FXEng%2Fstatus%2F1846605254864888180%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20X%20engineering%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3Bbig%20day%20for%20stalkers%20and%20harassers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20X%20user%20wrote%20in%20response%20to%20the%20announcement.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fevildeadthing%2Fstatus%2F1846611747727134945%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20got%20more%20than%2089%2C000%20likes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20blocking.%20It's%20supporting%20stalking%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FHeatherThomasAF%2Fstatus%2F1846662936242409668%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euser%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20do%20I%20block%20people%20whom%20I've%20blocked%20for%20security%20(stalking)%20reasons%3F%26quot%3B%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FBKatie617%2Fstatus%2F1846614222727196891%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euser%3C%2Fa%3E%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnything%20that%20gives%20an%20abusive%20individual%20power%20and%20control%20over%20the%20victim%20should%20be%20considered%20carefully%20by%20Twitter%2C%26quot%3B%20Adam%20Dodge%2C%20founder%20of%20End%20Tech-Enabled%20Abuse%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20mere%20knowledge%20that%20a%20person%20who%20is%20seeking%20to%20harm%20a%20victim%20can%20monitor%20their%20social%20media%20posts%20puts%20that%20victim%20in%20an%20unsafe%20position.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDodge%20said%20that%20this%20change%20in%20the%20block%20function%20could%20lead%20to%20some%20victims%20going%20into%20a%20mode%20of%20hypervigilence%2C%20which%20can%20have%20a%20severe%20impact%20on%20their%20emotional%20and%20physical%20wellbeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDodge%20said%20he%20expects%20some%20people%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20victims%20who%20criticize%20this%20change%20by%20telling%20them%20they%20should%20just%20make%20their%20account%20private%2C%20but%20he%20said%20that's%20blaming%20the%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20post%20about%20the%20change%2C%20X%20directed%20users%20who%20wanted%20more%20control%20over%20who%20could%20see%20their%20posts%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.x.com%2Fen%2Fsafety-and-security%2Fhow-to-make-x-private-and-public%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epage%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20explains%20how%20they%20can%20make%20their%20account%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDodge%20said%20victims%20should%20be%20able%20to%20have%20their%20account%20be%20public%20if%20they%20choose%2C%20and%20that%20they%20should%20be%20empowered%20to%20block%20users%20who%20are%20harassing%2C%20stalking%2C%20or%20abusing%20them.%20There%20are%20also%20people%20who%20need%20a%20public%20X%20account%20for%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20result%20in%20victims%20being%20forced%20to%20choose%20between%20safety%20and%20their%20right%20to%20speech%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20and%20we%20should%20nev