20contemporary%20pairs%2C%20simply%20cleaning%20them%20isn't%20always%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20typical%20surface%20dirt%2C%20oxidation%20is%20the%20biggest%20factor%20that%20can%20make%20a%20pair%20of%20sneakers%20look%20dingy%20and%20unappealing.%20You%20know%20when%20your%20white%20midsoles%20just%20won't%20come%20clean%20or%20when%20your%20icy%2C%20translucent%20outsoles%20turn%20that%20nasty%20yellow%3F%20That's%20oxidation%2C%20and%20usually%2C%20it's%20very%20hard%20to%20reverse.%20At%20least%2C%20that's%20what%20I%20thought%20before%20I%20tried%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D6381be9303b00de49a85c1b09b50a0fb4ecd2a46f842d60f6e2837cc0eee83b5%26postID%3D6712a034e5b54083005f1de5%26postSlug%3Dangelus-sole-bright-sneaker-restorer-brightener-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAngelus-Sole-Bright-4-Oz%252Fdp%252FB00METXKD4%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAngelus%20Sole%20Bright%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20%2413%20solution%20that%20can%20get%20rid%20of%20oxidation%20and%20restore%20your%20sneakers%20to%20their%20original%20glory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d5514f2-b810-4e99-90a2-8dabf556cb68%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20works%20and%20the%20supplies%20you'll%20need%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20Angelus%20Sole%20Bright%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20DIY%20project%2C%20but%20stick%20with%20me%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20easy%20to%20do%20and%20well%20worth%20the%20results.%20The%20restoring%20properties%20of%20Angelus%20Sole%20Bright%20are%20activated%20with%20UV%20rays.%20You%20can%20apply%20the%20solution%20to%20your%20shoes%20and%20use%20natural%20sunlight%2C%20but%20I%20highly%20recommend%20using%20an%20indoor%20grow%20lamp%20for%20a%20more%20controlled%20environment%20and%20better%20overall%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dea7bafcafb2aebcbdc3daa29060104cec99d2312fbcb16d0fc8fd20e560bc21a%26postID%3