lacing%20her%20ballot%20in%20the%202024%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20great-great-grandmother%20had%20previously%20been%20influenced%20by%20her%20late%20husband%2C%20who%20never%20voted.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe'd%20also%20felt%20held%20back%20by%20her%20illiteracy%20but%20said%20she's%20proud%20that%20her%20voice%20is%20finally%20being%20heard.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Betty%20Cartledge%2C%2081%2C%20from%20Covington%2C%20Georgia.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20delighted%20when%20a%20worker%20at%20my%20local%20early%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funique-polling-places-usa-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evoting%20station%3C%2Fa%3E%20gave%20me%20a%20sticker%20that%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20secured%20my%20vote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20put%20it%20on%20my%20coat%20and%20felt%20proud.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I'd%20voted%20in%20my%20life%2C%20I%20turn%2082%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%2C%20William%2C%20who%20died%20in%20April%20at%20the%20age%20of%2091%2C%20never%20voted%20either.%20We%20didn't%20really%20discuss%20it%20during%20our%2064%20years%20of%20marriage.%20I'm%20not%20exactly%20sure%20why%20he%20didn't%20vote%20himself%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20as%20if%20he%20told%20me%20I%20couldn't%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20the%20idea%20to%20vote%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%20after%20talking%20with%20my%20great-niece%20and%20a%20neighbor%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharris-trump-national-polls-election-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresidential%20election%20in%20November%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20like%20to%20vote%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20told%20them%2C%20%26quot%3B%20but%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20read%20or%20write.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seemed%20intimidat