%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22950%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESlaven%20Vlasic%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3B%20Chelsea%20Jia%20Feng%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBank%20of%20America%20analysts%20raised%20their%20price%20target%20for%20Nvidia%20stock%20to%20%24190%20a%20share%20this%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20see%20the%20AI%20market%20growing%20to%20%24400%20billion%2C%20giving%20Nvidia%20a%20%26quot%3Bgenerational%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20point%20to%20Nvidia's%20strong%20lead%20among%20competitors%2C%20helped%20by%20its%20enterprise%20partnerships.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20stock%20has%20been%20on%20a%20tear%20all%20year%2C%20but%20investors%20can%20brace%20for%20even%20more%20gains%20ahead%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%20analysts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Thursday%20note%2C%20the%20analysts%20raised%20their%20price%20objective%20on%20the%20stock%20from%20%24165%20to%20%24190.%20That%20implies%20a%2038%25%20upside%20from%20its%20price%20of%20about%20%24138%20a%20share%20at%20midday%20on%20Friday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20point%20to%20exponential%20growth%20in%20the%20AI%20market%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20which%20they%20say%20will%20give%20Nvidia%20a%20%26quot%3Bgenerational%20opportunity%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20chip%20titan%20continues%20to%20strengthen%20its%20lead%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20see%20the%20AI%20accelerator%20market%20growing%20to%20%24280%20billion%20by%202027%2C%20and%20toward%20upwards%20of%20%24400%20billion%20over%20time%20%E2%80%94%20marking%20huge%20growth%20from%20%2445%20billion%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20models%20continue%20to%20grow%20rapidly%E2%80%94with%20developers%20like%20OpenAI%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Meta%20launching%20new%20large%20language%20models%20several%20times%20per%20year%E2%80%94the%20need%20for%20computing%20will%20only%20grow%2C%20the%20analysts%20predict.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20new%20major%20LLM%20generation%2C%20especially%20those%20developed%20for%20larger%20size%20and%20better%20reasoning%20capabilities%2C%20will%20require%20greater%20training%20intensity%2C%20they%20add.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20to%20see%20the%20pace%20of%20new%20model%20development%20increase.%20LLMs%20in%20particular%20are%20being%20developed%20for%20both%20larger%20size%20and%20better%20reasoning%20capabilities%2C%20which%20both%20require%20greater%20training%20intensity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20point%20to%20Nvidia's%20strong%20partnerships%20with%20enterprise%20customers%20like%20Accenture%2C%20ServiceNow%2C%20Oracle%2C%20and%20others%2C%20which%20show%20the%20growing%20presence%20of%20AI%20at%20big%20companies%20and%20Nvidia's%20role%20as%20partner%20of%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNVDA's%20engagements%20span%20multiple%20verticals%20(e.g.%2C%20Accenture%2C%20ServiceNow%2C%20Microsoft)%2C%20and%20offerings%20such%20as%20AI%20Foundry%2C%20AI%20Hubs%2C%20NIMs%20are%20key%20levers%20to%20its%20AI%20leadership%2C%20not%20only%20on%20the%20hardware%20side%20but%20also%20on%20systems%2Fecosystems%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20also%20said%20Nvidia's%20financials%20are%20set%20up%20well%20for%20future%20gains.%20Given%20its%20free%20cash%20flow%20generation%20at%2045%25-50%25%20margins%2C%20which%20is%20nearly%20double%20that%20of%20other%20Magnificent%207%20stocks%2C%20Nvidia%20will%20be%20able%20to%20generate%20%24200%20billion%20in%20free%20cash%20flow%20over%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20stock%20has%20skyrocketed%20this%20year%2C%20up%20187%25%20as%20AI%20continues%20to%20boom%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-investors-wary-high-ai-spending-markets-selloff-nasdaq-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrief%20sell-off%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20