elhi'%20Suggestion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20chatter%20surrounding%20India's%20participation%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20which%20is%20scheduled%20to%20take%20place%20in%20Pakistan.%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20have%20not%20played%20a%20bilateral%20series%20in%20over%20a%20decade%20due%20to%20political%20tensions%20and%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20maintained%20a%20hard%20stance%20that%20the%20cricket%20team%20will%20not%20travel%20to%20Pakistan.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cricbuzz.com%2Fcricket-news%2F132088%2Fministers-visit-rekindles-talk-of-indias-participation-in-ct%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20has%20come%20up%20with%20a%20somewhat%20strange%20solution%20to%20the%20problem.%20The%20report%20claimed%20that%20PCB%20have%20written%20to%20BCCI%20%26quot%3Boffering%20assistance%C2%A0should%20the%20Indian%20team%20prefer%20to%20return%20to%20India%20-%20either%20to%20Chandigarh%20or%20New%20Delhi%20-%20after%20each%20game%20to%20avoid%20staying%20in%20Pakistan%20due%20to%20security%20concerns%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20current%20tournament%20schedule%2C%20India's%20three%20group%20stage%20matches%20are%20on%20-%20February%2020%20(vs%20Bangladesh)%2C%20February%2023%20(vs%20Pakistan)%2C%20and%20March%202%20(vs%20New%20Zealand).%20Moreover%2C%20they%20will%20all%20take%20place%20in%20Lahore%20-%20a%20venue%20that%20was%20reportedly%20chosen%20due%20to%20its%20proximity%20to%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20stated%20that%20there%20is%20nearly%20a%20week-long%20gap%20between%20India's%20last%20two%20matches%20and%20the%20PCB%20has%20suggested%20that%20India%20can%20travel%20back%20home%20during%20that%20time.%20However%2C%20in%20case%20India%20reach%20the%20final%20of%20the%20competition%2C%20Pakistan%20have%20maintained%20their%20stance%20of%20hosting%20the%20match%20in%20Lahore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20officials%20of%20the%20England%20and%20Wales%20Cricket%20Board%20(ECB)%2C%20including%20chairman%20Richard%20Thompson%2C%20have%20suggested%20that%20staging%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20without%20powerhouse%20India%20is%20not%20an%20option%20and%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bcontingencies%20available%26quot%3B%20if%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E's%20team%20doesn't%20travel%20to%20host%20country%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20not%20played%20in%20Pakistan%20since%202008%20due%20to%20the%20tense%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20and%20their%20travel%20to%20the%20South%20Asian%20nation%20is%20solely%20dependent%20on%20government%20clearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20government%20unlikely%20to%20give%20the%20BCCI%20permission%20to%20send%20the%20team%20to%20Lahore%2C%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20a%20hybrid%20model%20seems%20the%20most%20likely%20option.%20Like%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20last%20year%2C%20India%20can%20play%20their%20matches%20in%20a%20third%20country%20while%20the%20other%20games%20can%20be%20staged%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tournament%20will%20be%20held%20in%20February-March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20not%20be%20in%20cricket's%20interests%20for%20India%20not%20to%20be%20playing%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%26quot%3B%20Thompson%2C%20who%20is%20in%20Pakistan%20alongside%C2%A0ECB%C2%A0CEO%20Richard%20Gould%2C%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20ESPNcricinfo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729275000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fkq6tcivo_india-pakistan-match_625x300_18_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-to-not-stay-in-pakistan-during-champions-trophy-2025-pcb-gives-delhi-suggestio