20complainant%20in%20the%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%2C%20confirmed%20that%20this%20was%20the%20first%20FIR%20registered%20in%20the%20state%20under%20the%20newly%20enacted%20law%20against%20black%20magic%20and%20other%20such%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20new%20law%20came%20into%20effect%20on%20September%202%20through%20a%20gazette%20notification%2C%20and%20when%20we%20tried%20to%20upload%20the%20FIR%20on%20our%20eGujCop%20platform%20on%20October%2015%2C%20we%20learnt%20that%20no%20code%20was%20assigned%20to%20that%20Act.%20This%20proves%20that%20no%20FIRs%20were%20registered%20under%20it%20before%20this.%20A%20code%20was%20generated%20later%2C%20and%20we%20became%20the%20first%20police%20station%20to%20file%20an%20FIR%20under%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Godham%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2021%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20assembly%20passed%20the%20bill%20to%20curb%20the%20menace%20of%20black%20magic%20and%20other%20superstitious%20and%20inhuman%20practices.%20It%20became%20an%20Act%20after%20the%20governor%20gave%20his%20assent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20a%20person%20is%20seen%20performing%20rituals%20inside%20a%20crematorium%20run%20by%20the%20municipality%20in%20the%20Kumbharwada%20area.%20After%20some%20time%2C%20he%20circles%20a%20pyre%20and%20sleeps%20on%20it%20while%20reciting%20some%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20our%20investigation%2C%20we%20learnt%20that%20the%20person%20in%20the%20video%20was%20Ashwin%20Makwana%2C%20a%20sanitation%20worker.%20He%20uploaded%20the%20video%20on%20his%20Instagram%20account%20but%20deleted%20it%20after%20it%20went%20viral%20on%20WhatsApp.%20A%20local%20court%20has%20granted%20him%20bail%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20accused%20claimed%20that%20he%20always%20believed%20in%20tantric%20rituals%20and%20black%20magic%2C%20but%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20he%20performed%20such%20rituals%20in%20public%20and%20shot%20a%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMakwana%20wanted%20to%20create%20an%20impression%20that%20he%20possessed%20supernatural%20powers%20and%20knew%20black%20magic.%20He%20also%20wanted%20to%20teach%20a%20lesson%20to%20those%20who%20had%20made%20fun%20of%20his%20claims%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20offences%20under%20the%20Act%20are%20cognisable%20and%20non-bailable%2C%20Makwana%20was%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20court%20the%20next%20day%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Act%2C%20no%20person%20shall%20perform%20or%20even%20promote%20human%20sacrifice%20and%20other%20inhuman%2C%20evil%20and%20'aghori'%20practices%20and%20black%20magic%2C%20and%20a%20person%20found%20guilty%20of%20such%20offences%20will%20have%20to%20face%20imprisonment%20of%20six%20months%20to%20seven%20years%20with%20a%20fine%20ranging%20from%20Rs%205%2C000%20to%2050%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729274220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F0htt5beg_india-police-generic_625x300_23_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-1st-case-under-gujarat-black-magic-law-man-arrested-for-supernatural-powers-claim-6819350%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gujarat%20police%20have%20arrested%20a%2029-year-old%20man%20for%20allegedly%20performing%20some%20rituals%20inside%20a%20crematorium%20and%20sharing%20a%20video%20of%20it%20on%20social%20media%20claiming%20that%20he%20possessed%20supernatural%20powers%2C%20an%20official%20said%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-1st-case-under-gujarat-black-magic-law-man-arrested-for-supernatural-powers-claim-6819350%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel's%20Sinwar%20video%20shows%20the%20chilling%20reach%20of%20battlefield%20drones%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222550%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20screenshot%20from%20drone%20footage%20released%20by%20the%20IDF%20shows%20a%20blasted%20building%20where%20officials%20said%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20was%20hiding.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6712056d01ea6d83dee215a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221363%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20drone%20video%20released%20by%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20is%20said%20to%20capture%20the%20moments%20before%20the%20death%20of%20Hamas'%20leader%2C%20Yahya%20Sinwar.%3Cp%3EIsrael%20Defense%20Forces%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIsrael%20released%20a%20video%20on%20Thursday%20of%20what%20it%20said%20were%20Yahya%20Sinwar's%20final%20moments.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20clip%20shows%20a%20drone%20hovering%20near%20a%20dirt-covered%20figure%20as%20they%20throw%20an%20object%20at%20the%20camera.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20yet%20another%20display%20of%20how%20drones%20have%20radically%20changed%20wartime%20surveillance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20is%20chilling.%20A%20camera%20glides%20through%20the%20window%20of%20a%20ruined%20building%20scattered%20with%20wrecked%20furniture%20and%20hovers%20close%20to%20a%20lone%20figure%20in%20an%20armchair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20person%20caked%20in%20dust%2C%20their%20face%20obscured%20by%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eheadscarf%2C%20turns%20to%20face%20the%20drone%2C%20their%20right%20forearm%20clearly%20missing%20as%20though%20blown%20off%20by%20an%20explosive.%20The%20figure%20tosses%20an%20object%20resembling%20a%20stick%20toward%20the%20drone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%2C%20Israeli%20officials%20say%2C%20were%20the%20last%20moments%20of%20Hamas'%20leader%2C%20Yahya%20Sinwar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESinwar%20had%20hid%20from%20Israeli%20forces%20for%20more%20than%20a%20ye