were%20becoming%20ubiquitous%20even%20across%20impoverished%20areas%20back%20then.%20But%20a%20little%20over%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20the%20ability%20of%20armed%20groups%20to%20watch%20their%20adversaries%20has%20sped%20far%20past%20clips%20caught%20on%20phones%20and%20is%20spilling%20into%20public%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20have%20now%20flooded%20battlefields%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStandards%20for%20remote%20surveillance%2C%20once%20limited%20to%20still%20photos%20and%20grainy%20video%20from%20miles%20up%20in%20the%20sky%2C%20now%20revolve%20around%20cameras%20that%20can%20literally%20float%20a%20few%20feet%20away%20from%20a%20target%20like%20Sinwar%2C%20feeding%20live%20images%20back.%20This%20makes%20it%20possible%20to%20espy%20most%20enemy%20movements%20and%20sometimes%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20need%20for%20accurate%20surveillance%20stems%20from%20the%20development%20of%20long-range%20precision%20warfare%20over%20the%20past%2050%20to%2070%20years%2C%20said%20Mauro%20Gilli%2C%20a%20researcher%20in%20military%20technology%20and%20international%20security%20at%20the%20Swiss%20university%20ETH%20Zurich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20now%20possible%20to%20strike%20targets%20%26quot%3Bway%20beyond%20visual%20range%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20able%20to%20accurately%20identify%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhat%20you're%20about%20to%20strike%20becomes%20crucial%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20that's%20with%20daylight%20drone%20cameras%2C%20thermal%20imaging%2C%20radar%2C%20or%20electronic%20signals%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Sinwar%20video%2C%20the%20drone's%20position%20allowed%20combatants%20%26quot%3Bto%20approach%20a%20potentially%20threatening%20area%20without%20risk%20for%20the%20troops%2C%26quot%3B%20Gilli%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20drone%20operator%20and%20a%20drone%20in%20New%20York%2C%20Ukraine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b38f1743bb77284ba0b39d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmall%20drones%20are%20a%20critical%20feature%20of%20combat%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20where%20they've%20been%20used%20for%20battlefield%20observation%20and%20attacks.%20%3Cp%3EAnadolu%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf1f1b1f-2e95-4147-bb0e-f9a3d025b75a%5C%22%3EA%20dizzying%20proliferation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20become%20apparent%20that%20a%20human%20presence%20is%20no%20longer%20essential%20to%20tell%20us%20what's%20happening%20on%20the%20battlefield.%20Capabilities%20that%20had%20once%20been%20the%20sole%20preserve%20of%20top%20militaries%20like%20the%20US%20are%20spreading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20already%20a%20key%20feature%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20and%20Russian%20troops%20alike%20post%20dozens%20of%20drone%20videos%20a%20week%20to%20online%20forums%20and%20social%20media%2C%20showing%20clip%20after%20clip%20of%20ambushes%2C%20clashes%2C%20airstrikes%2C%20and%20artillery%20assaults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20more%20than%20just%20propaganda%20to%20try%20to%20rally%20the%20war's%20backers.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThink%20tanks%2C%20war%20experts%2C%20journalists%2C%20and%20governments%20alike%20now%20rely%20on%20drone%20footage%20as%20an%20everyday%20source%20of%20information%20%E2%80%94%20which%20still%20can%20be%20misleading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20drone%20game%20is%20just%20getting%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilitaries%20around%20the%20world%20are%20investing%20billions%20into%20their%20own%20arsenals%20of%20uncrewed%20aerial%20systems%2C%20spurred%20by%20the%20rapid%20emergence%20of%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20it%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20with%20all%20the%20high%20tech%20from%20semiconductors%2C%20microelectronics%2C%20you%20name%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Gilli%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20these%20technologies%2C%20they%20have%20become%20much%20more%20powerful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hovering%20quality%20of%20the%20Sinwar%20video%20indicates%20it%20was%20filmed%20by%20a%20quadcopter.%20These%20drones%2C%20popular%20with%20photographers%20and%20racers%2C%20often%20cost%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20and%20have%20advanced%20so%20rapidly%20that%20they%20have%20military%20uses.%20Unlike%20soaring%20fixed-wing%20drones%2C%20quadcopters%20can%20fly%20into%20bunkers%20and%20buildings%20via%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20skilled%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20plans%20to%20spend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fpentagon%2F2024%2F03%2F11%2Fpentagon-says-1-billion-planned-for-first-two-years-of-replicator%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20next%20two%20years%20on%20low-cost%20drones.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Ukraine%20said%20it%20was%20setting%20up%20what%20is%20likely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-setting-up-separate-military-branch-focused-drone-warfare-russia-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20world's%20first%20military%20branch%3C%2Fa%3E%20devoted%20solely%20to%20drone%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20that%20Ukraine%20had%20procured%20and%20delivered%201%20million%20drones%20to%20the%20battlefield%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funited24media.com%2Flatest-news%2Fukraine-delivers-one-million-state-funded-drones-to-frontline-3017%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Ukrainian%20state%20media%20outlet%20United24%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoscow%2C%20too%2C%20has%20pledged%20to%20produce%20millions%20of%20first-person%20drones%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommentators%20have%20already%20begun%20asking%20whether%20even%20that%20number%20will%20be%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaria%20Berlinska%2C%20a%20drone%20operator%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20volunteer%20drone-training%20project%20Victory%20Drones%2C%20estimated%20that%20Ukraine%20would%20need%20four%20times%20that%20many%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftsn.ua%2Fato%2Fchi-vistachit-ukrayini-milyona-droniv-berlinska-zdivuvala-pidrahunkami-2669805.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20local%20outlet%20TCH%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drone%20Pilot%20Maya%20O'Daly%20on%20July%2030%2C%202019%2C%20at%20an%20army%20base%20in%20the%20South%20of%20Israel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e26c5b4abc992e8c7ebe1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIsraeli%20troops%20have%20trained%20to%20fly%20small%20drones%20like%20this%20quadcopter.%3Cp%3EGuy%20Prives%20%7C%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213d0916e-7a81-4e4a-bf51-4ab2277d6b5e%5C%22%3EThe%20'transparent'%20battlefield%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sheer%20volume%20of%20reconnaissance%20and%20exploding%20drones%20has%20profound%20implications%20that%20are%20far%20from%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20astounding%20wealth%20of%20drone-fed%20intelligence%2C%20surveillance%2C%20and%20reconnaissance%20has%20made%20more%20of%20the%20battlefield%20visible%20than%20ever%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20shock%20incursion%20into%20Russia's%20Kursk%20region%20on%20August%206%20has%20challenged%20those%20who%20argue%20the%20increasingly%20%26quot%3Btransparent%26quot%3B%20battlefield%20makes%20surprise%20nearly%20impossible%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foe.tradoc.army.mil%2F2024%2F09%2F19%2Fhow-ukraine-overcame-the-transparent-battlefield-to-achieve-operational-surprise-in-kursk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20US%20Army%20assessment%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20attack%20said.%20Another%20example%20is%20that%20Israel's%20military%20failed%20to%20recognize%20preparations%20for%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20desp