0India%20for%20Rs%204%2C051%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729273745000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fjsw-steel-jfe-steel-corp-jv-to-buy-tkes-india-for-rs-4-051-crore-124101801221_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20transaction%20is%20being%20undertaken%20by%20Jsquare%2C%20a%20wholly%20owned%20subsidiary%20of%20JSW%20JFE%20Electrical%20Steel%20Private%20Limited%20(J2ES)%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hamas%20Searching%20For%20Yahya%20Sinwar's%20Replacement%20Outside%20Gaza%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20operator%20group%20Hamas%20will%20likely%20replace%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20with%20a%20new%20political%20leader%20based%20outside%20Gaza%20while%20his%20brother%20-%20Mohammad%20Sinwar%20-%20is%20expected%20to%20assume%20a%20bigger%20role%20directing%20the%20war%20against%20Israel%20in%20the%20territory%2C%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20leadership%20deliberations%2C%20Hamas%20must%20consider%20not%20only%20the%20preferences%20of%20its%20main%20backer%20-%20Iran%20-%20but%20also%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20Gulf%20Arab%20state%20of%20Qatar%2C%20where%20all%20the%20main%20candidates%20to%20take%20over%20as%20politburo%20chief%20currently%20reside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinwar%2C%20a%20mastermind%20of%20the%20October%207%2C%202023%20attack%20that%20ignited%20the%20devastating%20Gaza%20war%2C%20was%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20in%20a%20gunbattle%20on%20Wednesday%20--%20the%20second%20time%20in%20less%20than%20three%20months%20that%20Hamas%20has%20lost%20its%20top%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20previous%20chief%2C%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%2C%20was%20assassinated%20in%20Iran%20in%20July%20almost%20certainly%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sinwar%20replaced%20him%2C%20he%20fused%20together%20both%20the%20military%20and%20political%20leadership%20in%20Gaza%2C%20but%20that%20does%20not%20appear%20likely%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20more%20than%20a%20year%20of%20ferocious%20Israeli%20attacks%20that%20have%20pounded%20Hamas%2C%20killed%20thousands%20of%20its%20fighters%20and%20eliminated%20senior%20figures%20both%20inside%20and%20out%20of%20Gaza%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20how%20the%20Islamist%20group%20will%20emerge%20from%20this%20latest%20blow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinwar's%20deputy%20Khalil%20Al-Hayya%2C%20who%20is%20viewed%20as%20a%20potential%20successor%2C%20struck%20a%20defiant%20note%20on%20Friday%2C%20saying%20Israeli%20hostages%20would%20not%20be%20returned%20until%20Israeli%20troops%20withdrew%20from%20Gaza%20and%20the%20war%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20a%20history%20of%20quickly%20and%20efficiently%20replacing%20its%20fallen%20leaders%2C%20with%20its%20top%20decision-making%20body%2C%20the%20Shura%20Council%2C%20tasked%20with%20naming%20a%20new%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shura%20Council%20represents%20all%20Hamas%20members%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20Israeli%20prisons%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20community%2C%20meaning%20the%20new%20leader%20should%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20enter%20ceasefire%20talks%20even%20if%20he%20is%20not%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20Hamas%20gunmen%20still%20hold%20dozens%20of%20Israelis%20hostage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Hayya%2C%20who%20is%20Hamas'%20chief%20negotiator%2C%20the%20other%20main%20leadership%20contenders%20are%20Khaled%20Meshaal%2C%20Haniyeh's%20predecessor%2C%20and%20Mohammad%20Darwish%2C%20a%20little-known%20figure%20who%20chairs%20the%20Shura%20Council%2C%20according%20to%20analysts%20and%20a%20Hamas%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20will%20need%20to%20notify%20Qatar%2C%20which%20has%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20rounds%20of%20so%20far%20fruitless%20ceasefire%20talks%2C%20and%20other%20regional%20capitals%20ahead%20of%20its%20decision%2C%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDividing%20Duties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshraf%20Abouelhoul%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20Palestinian%20affairs%2C%20expected%20Sinwar's%20responsibilities%20to%20be%20split%20between%20two%20roles%20-%20one%20overseeing%20military%20affairs%20and%20another%20running%20the%20political%20office%2C%20responsible%20for%20international%20contacts%20and%20shaping%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIran%20is%20Hamas%20strongest%20ally%2C%20which%20supports%20the%20group%20with%20money%20and%20weapons%2C%20and%20their%20blessing%20is%20key%20to%20who%20becomes%20Sinwar's%20successor%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Abouelhoul%2C%20managing%20editor%20of%20the%20state-owned%20newspaper%20Al-Ahram%20in%20Egypt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20expected%20Hamas%20to%20stick%20by%20core%20demands%20in%20future%20ceasefire%20talks%2C%20chiefly%20that%20Israeli%20forces%20withdraw%20from%20Gaza%20and%20stop%20the%20war.%20But%20it%20could%20show%20more%20flexibility%20on%20some%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20the%20details%20of%20any%20deal%20swapping%20Israeli%20hostages%20for%20Palestinians%20imprisoned%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20declared%20Sinwar's%20killing%20a%20milestone%20but%20that%20the%20war%20is%20not%20yet%20over%2C%20saying%20fighting%20would%20continue%20until%20the%20hostages%20are%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20was%20founded%20in%201987%20and%20is%20a%20branch%20of%20the%20Sunni%20Islamist%20Muslim%20Brotherhood%20movement.%20Its%20decisions%20are%20usually%20taken%20through%20consensus%20in%20Hamas%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Sinwar%20dead%2C%20the%20Hamas%20leadership%20for%20Gaza%20has%20temporarily%20passed%20to%20his%20Qatar-based%20deputy%2C%20Hayya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20ongoing%20war%20and%20communication%20difficulties%20might%20impose%20limits%20on%20just%20how%20much%20day-to-day%20contact%20Hayya%20can%20have%20with%20men%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20leaving%20the%20armed%20wing%20-%20the%20Qassam%20Brigades%20-%20in%20the%20driving%20seat%2C%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Hamas%20source%20said%20Hayya%20was%20expected%20to%20encounter%20no%20problems%20exercising%20his%20role%20as%20%26quot%3Bde%20facto%20Gaza%20leader%26quot%3B.%20The%20source%20noted%20that%20Hayya%20had%20maintained%20good%20relations%20with%20the%20military%20wing%20and%20had%20been%20close%20to%20both%20Sinwar%20and%20Haniyeh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkram%20Attallah%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20political%20analyst%2C%20said%20he%20expected%20the%20armed%20wing%20to%20respect%20Hayya's%20authority%20-%20even%20from%20afar.%20He%20also%20expected%20Mohammad%20Sinwar%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20more%20significant%20figure%20in%20the%20armed%20wing%20and%20in%20Hamas%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20veteran%20commander%20of%20the%20Qassam%20Brigades%2C%20Mohammad%20Sinwar%20has%20seldom%20appeared%20in%20public%2C%20has%20long%20been%20on%20Israel's%20most-wanted%20list%20and%20has%20survived%20several%20attempts%20on%20his%20life%2C%20Hamas%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas-led%20gunmen%20killed%201%2C200%20people%20and%20abducted%20another%20250%20during%20the%20Oct.%207%20attack%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20tallies.%20This%20prompted%20an%20Israeli%20offensive%20which%2C%20according%20to%20Palestinian%20authorities%2C%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2042%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20laid%20waste%20to%20Gaza%2C%20and%20driven%20nearly%20all%20its%20population%20from%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinwar's%20appointment%20in%20August%20was%20seen%20as%20both%20a%20show%20of%20defiance%20and%20internal%20unity%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20close%20ties%20to%20Iran%20were%20seen%20as%20a%20factor%20supporting%20his%20candidacy.%20Both%20Darwish%20and%20Hayya%20are%20also%20seen%20as%20close%20to%20Tehran%2C%20whose%20support%20will%20be%20vital%20for%20Hamas%2