hit%20Ivory%20Coast%20student%20union%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729267877000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1752%2Flive%2F1c77d250-8d66-11ef-8e6d-e3e64e16c628.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9qvzjpz18po%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22All%20student%20unions%20are%20banned%20after%20the%20authorities%20accuse%20one%20of%20murder%2C%20torture%20and%20running%20a%20brothel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9qvzjpz18po%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9qvzjpz18po.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9qvzjpz18po.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BChild%20Marriage%20Deprives%20Children%20Of%20Agency%2C%20Autonomy%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIssuing%20a%20slew%20of%20directions%20for%20the%20effective%20implementation%20of%20the%20Prohibition%20of%20Child%20Marriage%20Act%2C%202006%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20said%20that%20child%20marriage%20deprives%20children%20of%20their%20agency%2C%20autonomy%2C%20and%20right%20to%20fully%20develop%20and%20enjoy%20their%20childhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%2C%20headed%20by%20CJI%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20ordered%20state%20and%20Union%20Territory%20governments%20to%20appoint%20officers%20solely%20responsible%20for%20discharging%20the%20functions%20of%20Child%20Marriage%20Prohibition%20Officers%20(CMPOs)%20at%20the%20district%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20officers%20should%20not%20be%20burdened%20with%20additional%20duties%20that%20could%20impede%20their%20focus%20on%20preventing%20child%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justices%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20was%20dealing%20with%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20(PIL)%20raising%20the%20grievance%20that%20the%20rate%20of%20child%20marriages%20in%20India%20is%20alarming%20despite%20the%20enactment%20of%20the%202006%20Act.%20The%20PIL%20highlighted%20the%20practice%20of%20appointing%20an%20officer%20with%20multifarious%20duties%20as%20the%20CMPO%20impeded%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20child%20marriage%20prevention%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20judgment%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20noted%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20appointment%20of%20CMPOs%20is%20not%20a%20mere%20statutory%20formality%20as%20part%20of%20an%20ornate%20virtue%20signalling.%20An%20effective%20CMPO%20must%20make%20efforts%20to%20find%20their%20roots%20in%20the%20community%2C%20engage%20with%20communities%20and%20organisations%20in%20the%20area%20and%20carry%20out%20the%20painstaking%2C%20and%20sometimes%20thankless%2C%20task%20of%20reporting%20specific%20factors%20affecting%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20district.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20ordered%2C%20that%20given%20the%20significant%20obligations%20expected%20to%20be%20discharged%20by%20a%20dedicated%20CMPO%2C%20no%20officer%20with%20other%20responsibilities%20should%20be%20appointed%20to%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStates%20or%20UTs%20shall%20appoint%20exclusive%20CMPOs%20in%20each%20district%20in%20addition%20to%20any%20CMPOs%20already%20serving%20in%20a%20dual%20capacity%2C%20and%20they%20shall%20equip%20these%20officers%20with%20adequate%20resources%20for%20the%20effective%20discharge%20of%20their%20functions%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20said%20that%20a%20state%20government%20or%20UT%20administration%20may%20file%20an%20application%20before%20it%20seeking%20permission%20to%20appoint%20a%20CMPO%20who%20also%20holds%20other%20duties%20if%20instances%20of%20child%20marriage%20have%20decreased%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20appointing%20exclusive%20CMPOs%20is%20no%20longer%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PIL%20filed%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20sought%20stronger%20enforcement%20mechanisms%2C%20awareness%20programmes%2C%20and%20comprehensive%20support%20systems%20for%20child%20brides%20to%20ensure%20the%20protection%20and%20welfare%20of%20vulnerable%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20judgment%2C%20the%20court%20said%20that%20the%20collectors%20and%20superintendents%20of%20police%20in%20each%20district%20across%20India%20will%20also%20be%20responsible%20for%20actively%20preventing%20child%20marriages%20within%20their%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20shall%20have%20the%20authority%20and%20responsibility%20to%20prosecute%20all%20individuals%20who%20facilitate%20or%20solemnise%20child%20marriages%2C%20including%20those%20who%20knowingly%20assist%2C%20promote%2C%20or%20bless%20such%20marriages%2C%20even%20if%20reported%20in%20public%20events%20or%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20it%20suggested%20that%20the%20state%20governments%20consider%20the%20viability%20of%20integrating%20the%20Special%20Juvenile%20Police%20Unit%20into%20the%20child%20marriage%20prevention%20framework%20to%20manage%20cases%20of%20child%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20all%20magistrates%20to%20take%20proactive%20measures%2C%20including%20issuing%20suo%20motu%20injunctions%20to%20prevent%20the%20solemnisation%20of%20child%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMagistrates%20are%20encouraged%20to%20particularly%20focus%20on%20'auspicious%20days'%20known%20for%20mass%20weddings%2C%20when%20the%20occurrence%20of%20child%20marriages%20is%20notably%20high.%20Upon%20receiving%20credible%20information%20or%20even%20upon%20suspicion%2C%20Magistrates%20should%20use%20their%20judicial%20powers%20to%20halt%20such%20marriages%20and%20ensure%20child%20protection%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20suggested%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20in%20coordination%20with%20state%20governments%2C%20assess%20the%20feasibility%20of%20establishing%20special%20fast-track%20courts%20exclusively%20to%20handle%20child%20marriage%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20courts%20will%20expedite%20case%20proceedings%2C%20thereby%20preventing%20prolonged%20delays%20that%20often%20lead%20to%20additional%20harm%20for%20the%20affected%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20ordered%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20and%20the%20National%20Legal%20Services%20Authority%20(NALSA)%2C%20to%20set%20up%20a%20designated%20portal%20for%20online%20reporting%20of%20child%20marriages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20portal%20will%20include%20features%20for%20anonymous%20reporting%2C%20allowing%20victims%20and%20concerned%20citizens%20to%20easily%20lodge%20complaints%20and%20access%20support%20services%20and%20serve%20as%20a%20centralised%20platform%20for%20collecting%20and%20analysing%20data%20on%20child%20marriage%20incidents%2C%20enabling%20targeted%20interventions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20suggested%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20consider%20the%20viability%20of%20providing%20compensation%20to%20girls%20who%20opt%20out%20of%20marriage%20upon%20reaching%20the%20age%20of%20majority%20under%20the%20NALSA%20Victim%20Compensation%20Scheme%20or%20State%20Victim%20Compensation%20Schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20compensation%20should%20be%20equivalent%20to%20that%20provided%20to%20rape%20victims%2C%20ensuring%20adequate%20support%20for%20those%20who%20have%20escaped%20child%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20detailed%20141-page%20verdict%2C%20the%20top%20court%20stressed%20that%20despite%20progress%20in%20awareness%20campaigns%2C%20there%20is%20still%20a%20pressing%20need%20to%20enhance%20accountability%20mechanisms%2C%20ensure%20mandatory%20reporting%2C%20and%20rehabilitate%20minors%20affected%20by%20child%20marriages.%20It%20said%20that%20girls%20who%20are%20married%20off%20early%20are%20not%20only%20denied%20their%20childhood%20but%20left%20to%20the%20mercies%20of%20their%20marital%20home%20and%20in-laws%2C%20adding%20that%20boys%20who%20are%20married%20early%20are%20forced%20to%20take%20up%20more%20responsibilities%20and%20are%20pressured%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20a%20provider%20to%20the%20family%2C%20earlier%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20sexes%20are%20adversely%20affected%20by%20forced%20and%20early%20marriage.%20Marrying%20in%20childhood%20has%20the%20effect%20of%20objectifying%20the%20child.%20The%20practice%20of%20child%20marriage%20imposes%20mature%20burdens%20on%20children%20who%20are%20not%20physically%20or%20mentally%20prepared%20to%20comprehend%20the%20significance%20of%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729267800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F6f5n98uo_supreme-court_625x300_03_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeprives-children-of-rights-sc-issues-directions-for-effective-implementation-of-prohibition-of-child-marriage-act-6819126%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Issuing%20a%20slew%20of%20directions%20for%20the%20effective%20implementation%20of%20the%20Prohibition%20of%20Child%20Marriage%20Act%2C%202006%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20that%20child%20marriage%20deprives%20children%20of%20their%20agency%2C%20autonomy%2C%20and%20right%20to%20fully%20develop%20and%20enjoy%20their%20childhood%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeprives-children-of-rights-sc-issues-directions-for-effective-implementation-of-prohibition-of-child-marriage-act-6819126%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MK%20Stalin%20Asks%20Centre%20To%20Recall%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Governor%20In%20Row%20Over%20Anthem%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETensions%20between%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20and%20governor%20rose%20significantly%20on%20Friday%20after%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20said%20a%20line%20with%20the%20word%20'Dravida'%20was%20skipped%20when%20the%20Tamil%20anthem%20was%20sung%20at%20an%20event%20attended%20by%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi.%20Asking%20the%20Centre%20to%20recall%20the%20governor%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20accused%20him%20of%20insulting%20national%20unity%20and%20Mr%20Ravi%20hit%20back%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20had%20made%20a%20racist%20remark%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20skipping%20of%20the%20line%20added%20fuel%20to%20a%20raging%20fire%20over%20the%20Centre%20celebrating%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20Hindi%20month%20along%20with%20the%20golden%20jubilee%20celebrations%20of%20Chennai%20Doordarshan%20-%20the%20event%20attended%20by%20Mr%20Ravi.%20Chief%20Minister%20Stalin%20had%20objected%20to%20this%20and%20said%20celebrating%20Hindi%20in%20a%20non-Hindi-speaking%20state%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20belittle%20other%20languages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20anthem%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Thaai%20Vazhthu%2C%20is%20sung%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20every%20government%20programme%20and%20the%20word%20'Dravida'%20largely%20refers%20to%20the%20racial%20identity%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20southern%20states.%20The%20group%20from%20Doordarshan%2C%20while%20singing%20the%20anthem%2C%20left%20out%20the%20line%20which%20has%20the%20word%20in%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoordarshan%20Tamil%20has%20apologised%20for%20the%20line%20being%20skipped%20and%20blamed%20the%20mistake%20on%20the%20singers%20being%20distracted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20governor%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%2C%20said%20Mr%20Ravi%20is%20%26quot%3Bunfit%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20post%20and%20asked%20whether%20he%20would%20call%20for%20'Dravida'%20being%20skipped%20in%20the%20national%20anthem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20skipping%20the%20word%20in%20the%20Tamil%20anthem%20violates%20the%20state's%20law%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20accused%20the%20governor%20of%20insulting%20national%20unity%20and%20the%20people%20of%20many%20races%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20celebrating%20Hindi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20the%20governor%20who%20suffers%20from%20a%20Dravidian%20allergy%20ask%20them%20to%20leave%20out%20'Dravida'%20in%20the%20national%20anthem%3F%20The%20Union%20Government%20should%20immediately%20recall%20the%20Governor%20who%20is%20deliberately%20insulting%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20wrote%20in%20Tamil%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20strong%20rejoinder%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20Mr%20Ravi%20said%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20a%20racist%20remark%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20governor%20is%20%26quot%3Bunfortunately%20cheap%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHon'ble%20Chief%20Minister%20Thiru.%20%40mkstalin%20has%20issued%20a%20regrettable%20tweet%20this%20evening%20in%20which%20he%20made%20a%20racist%20remark%20against%20me%20and%20levelled%20false%20allegation%20of%20showing%20disrespect%20to%20Tamizh%20Thaai%20Vaazhthu.%20He%20knows%20it%20well%20that%20I%20recite%20full%20Tamizh%20Thaai%20Vaazhthu%20at%20every%20function%20and%20do%20so%20with%20reverence%2C%20pride%20and%20precision%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20governor%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ravi%20asserted%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20taken%20several%20steps%20for%20the%20promotion%20of%20Tamil%20culture%20and%20heritage%20and%20so%20has%20he.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaking%20racist%20remark%20and%20alleging%20incorrect%20imputations%20against%20governor%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20unfortunately%20cheap%20and%20lowers%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20high%20constitutional%20office%20of%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Since%20he%20rushed%20to%20public%20with%20his%20racist%20remarks%20and%20false%20imputations%20I%20am%20constrained%20to%20respond%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor-turned-politician%20Kamal%20Haasan%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Makkal%20Needhi%20Maiam%20(MNM)%20party%2C%20also%20condemned%20the%20incident%20without%20naming%20the%20governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDravidian%20has%20a%20place%20not%20only%20in%20the%20Tamil%20anthem%20but%20also%20in%20the%20National%20Anthem.%20Leaving%20out%20the%20words%20'Dravidian%20Nalthirunadu'%20and%20singing%20it%2C%20thinking%20that%20it%20is%20politics%2C%20is%20an%20act%20of%20insulting%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20laws%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20and%20the%20world's%20oldest%20language%2C%20Tamil%2C%20which%20is%20the%20pride%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hassan%20wrote%20in%20Tamil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Doordarshan%20Tamil%20apologised%20for%20the%20mistake%20and%20blamed%20it%20on%20distracted%20singers.%20It%20said%20there%20was%20no%20intent%20to%20disrespect%20Tamil%20or%20the%20Tamil%20anthem%20and%20also%20apologised%20to%20the%20governor%20for%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHindi%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20had%20written%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20about%20the%20Golden%20Jubilee%20Celebrations%20of%20Chennai%20Doordarshan%20being%20combined%20with%20Hindi%20Month%20Celebrations%20and%20said%20celebrating%20%26quot%3Bsuch-Hindi%20language%20oriented%20events%20in%20non-Hindi%20speaking%20states%26quot%3B%20can%20be%20avoided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20are%20aware%2C%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20does%20not%20accord%20national%20language%20status%20to%20any%20language.%20Hindi%20and%20English%20are%20used%20only%20for%20official%20purposes%20such%20as%20legislation%2C%20judiciary%20and%20communication%20between%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20state%20governments.%20In%20the%20circumstances%2C%20in%20a%20multilingual%20country%20like%20India%2C%20according%20special%20place%20to%20Hindi%20and%20celebrating%20Hindi%20Month%20in%20non-Hindi%20speaking%20States%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20belittle%20other%20languages%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20I%20suggest%20that%20holding%20such%20Hindi%20language-oriented%20events%20in%20non-Hindi%20speaking%20States%20could%20be%20avoided%20or%20if%20the%20Union%20government%20still%20desires%20to%20hold%20such%20events%2C%20I%20suggest%20that%20celebration%20of%20the%20local%20language%20month%20in%20respective%20states%20must%20also%20be%20done%20with%20equal%20warmth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20Ravi%20said%20Hindi%20should%20not%20be%20viewed%20as%20an%20imposition%20but%20as%20a%20language%20to%20be%20celebrated%20alongside%20other%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20when%20I%20came%20here%2C%20Hindi%20was%20not%20a%20welcome%20language%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20but%20when%20I%20started%20meeting%20students%2C%20I%20was%20happily%20surprised%20that%20their%20Hindi%20was%20better%20than%20mine.%20There%20is%20a%20greater%20acceptance%20of%20Hindi%20among%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu...%20Hindi%20is%20not%20a%20language%20of%20imposition%20of%20language%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governor%20also%20expressed%20concern%20over%20what%20he%20called%20an%20attempt%20to%20isolate%20Tamil%20Nadu%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20India%2C%20describing%20such%20efforts%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btoxic%20and%20separatist%20policy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20perceived%20imposition%20of%20Hindi%20has%20led%20to%20several%20agitations%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20the%20past%20and%20remains%20a%20social%20and%20political%20issue%20that%20comes%20up%20from%20time%20to%20time%20in%20the%20state%20and%20other%20southern%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK-led%20government%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20the%20governor%20have%20clashed%20several%20times%20over%20pending%20bills%2C%20the%20Dravidian%20model%20of%20governance%20and%20Mr%20Ravi's%20remarks.%20In%20March%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20had%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20over%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20minister%20and%C2%A0accused%20Mr%20Ravi%20of%20%26quot%3Battempting%20to%20run%20a%20parallel%20government%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729267800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm106lobc_mk-stalin-ians_625x300_29_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmk-stalin-asks-centre-to-recall-tamil-nadu-governor-in-row-over-anthem-6819349%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tensions%20between%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20and%20governor%20rose%20significantly%20on%20Friday%20after%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20said%20a%20line%20with%20the%20word%20'Dravida'%20was%20skipped%20when%20the%20Tamil%20anthem%20was%20sung%20at%20an%20event%20attended%20by%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmk-stalin-asks-centre-to-recall-tamil-nadu-governor-in-row-over-anthem-6819349%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Camila%20Cabello%20mourns%20Liam%20Payne%3A%20'It's%20a%20tragedy..'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729267279