s%20impractical.%20Roads%20should%20be%20built%20well...%20we%20can't%20say%20they%20should%20be%20better%20than%20America...%20but%20quality%20roads%20should%20be%20the%20focus.%20We%20follow%20the%20Indian%20Road%20Congress%20guidelines%20for%20road%20construction%2C%20and%20seminars%20are%20organised%20for%20such%20discussions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeginning%20on%20Saturday%2C%20a%20two-day%20brainstorming%20seminar%20will%20be%20held%20at%20the%20Ravindra%20Bhavan%20in%20Bhopal%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20improving%20the%20quality%20of%20road%20and%20bridge%20construction%20and%20ensuring%20the%20use%20of%20new%20technologies%20to%20build%20stronger%20infrastructure%20within%20deadlines.%20The%20seminar%20is%20being%20organised%20by%20the%20Indian%20Road%20Congress%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Public%20Works%20Department%20and%20it%20will%20also%20be%20attended%20by%20Union%20Road%20Transport%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20speaking%20at%20the%20Pandit%20Deendayal%20Upadhyaya%20Forum%20launch%20in%20Washington%20DC%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%2C%20who%20was%20the%20longest-serving%20chief%20minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20is%20now%20the%20agriculture%20minister%2C%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20landed%20at%20the%20airport%20in%20Washington%20and%20drove%20on%20the%20roads%2C%20I%20felt%20that%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20roads%20are%20better%20than%20the%20US...%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20this%20just%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chouhan%20had%20also%20said%20that%20his%20government%20had%20constructed%201.75%20lakh%20km%20of%20roads%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20connected%20all%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729265460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fbllbejrg_potholes-on-road-madhya-pradesh_625x300_18_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshiv