-of-Cover-image-94-min-1729257164-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-94-min-1729257164-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-94-min-1729257164-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371252%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESeveral%20local%20women%20find%20employment%20at%20Anuskha%E2%80%99s%20farm%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20a%20desk%20job.%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20at%20the%20ground%20level.%20Even%20when%20I%20tried%20learning%20French%2C%20something%20felt%20amiss.%20I%20aimed%20to%20inspire%20people%20and%20provide%20them%20with%20livelihoods%20and%20skills%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anushka%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20researched%20agriculture%2C%20she%20was%20adamant%20about%20avoiding%20traditional%20farming%20due%20to%20its%20myriad%20challenges%2C%20such%20as%20poor%20yields%2C%20pest%20infestations%2C%20and%20crop%20losses%20caused%20by%20unpredictable%20weather.%20With%20climate%20change%20further%20complicating%20matters%2C%20she%20found%20her%20ideal%20path%20in%20protected%20cultivation%20and%20horticulture.%20A%20course%20in%20horticulture%2C%20followed%20by%20training%20in%20mushroom%20cultivation%20at%20the%20Institute%20of%20Mushroom%20Research%20in%20Solan%2C%20gave%20wings%20to%20her%20dreams.%20She%20learnt%20protected%20cultivation%2C%20hydroponics%2C%20horticulture%2C%20and%20more%20through%20various%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20growing%20plants%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment%2C%20farmers%20can%20get%20a%20stable%20yield%20and%20quality%20produce%2C%20safeguarded%20from%20adverse%20climatic%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20his%20knowledge%2C%20Anushka%20started%20farming%20on%20an%20