%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20journey%2C%20like%20any%20entrepreneur%2C%20has%20been%20filled%20with%20ups%20and%20downs%20and%20a%20steep%20learning%20curve.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20doubted%20me%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20as%20I%20was%20just%2024%20when%20I%20started.%20They%20weren%E2%80%99t%20used%20to%20a%20woman%20practising%20this%20new%20form%20of%20cultivation.%20Most%20farmers%20in%20this%20area%20are%20men.%20My%20family%20was%20my%20biggest%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quality%20of%20her%20produce%20added%20with%20her%20work%20ethic%20silenced%20critics.%20However%2C%20creating%20the%20necessary%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20is%20capital-intensive%2C%20posed%20additional%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20challenge%20has%20been%20the%20lack%20of%20good%20trainers%20in%20the%20field.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20matter%20how%20many%20courses%20one%20takes%2C%20things%20are%20very%20different%20practically%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20aims%20to%20change%20this%20by%20helping%20people%20set%20up%20similar%20farms.%20Her%20farm%20welcomes%20visitors%2C%20and%20Anushka%20is%20always%20up%20for%20sharing%20her%20knowledge.%20What%20helped%20her%2C%20she%20stresses%2C%20was%20a%20deep%20commitment%20to%20the%20subject.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20initial%20year%2C%20she%20dedicated%20countless%20hours%20to%20ensuring%20everything%20was%20perfect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilt%20from%20scratch%2C%20she%20also%20cultivates%20crops%20for%20individuals%20who%20lack%20the%20time%20to%20manage%20their%20own%20farms.%20Finding%20the%20right%20team%20is%20crucial%2C%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20fortunate%20to%20find%20excellent%20people.%20Today%2C%20they%20can%20run%20the%20farm%20by%20themselves%20even%20in%20my%20absence%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20vision%2