0women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20NDA%20was%20leading%20in%2052%20assembly%20segments%20(BJP%2047%2C%20AJSU%20five)%2C%20while%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20ahead%20in%2029%20seats%20(Congress%2015%2C%20JMM%2014).%20The%20simple%20majority%20mark%20is%2041.%20While%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20not%20always%20indicative%20of%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20outcomes%2C%20they%20provide%20a%20recent%20reference%20point%20since%20the%20last%20state%20elections%20were%20held%20five%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Modi%20Premium'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BModi%20premium%26quot%3B%20that%20benefits%20the%20BJP%20in%20national%20elections%20tends%20to%20diminish%20at%20the%20state%20level%2C%20as%20observed%20in%20the%20past.%20Although%20the%20NDA%20won%20nine%20of%20the%2014%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20it%20lost%20three%20seats%20compared%20to%202019%2C%20while%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20captured%20five%2C%20sweeping%20all%20the%20ST-reserved%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHemant%20Soren's%20arrest%20by%20the%20ED%20appears%20to%20have%20evoked%20sympathy%20and%20consolidated%20support%20among%20the%20ST%20community%2C%20at%20least%20in%20reserved%20seats.%20However%2C%20this%20sympathy%20did%20not%20extend%20to%20other%20caste%20or%20demographic%20groups%2C%20including%20the%2030%25%20of%20Jharkhand's%20population%20made%20up%20mainly%20of%20Biharis%2C%20Bengalis%2C%20and%20residents%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20maintained%20its%20support%20among%20upper%20castes%2C%20OBCs%2C%20and%20SCs.%20The%20ST-reserved%20seats%20have%20historically%20been%20a%20weak%20point%20for%20the%20BJP%3B%20it%20won%20only%20two%20of%20the%2028%20reserved%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20assembly%20elections%20and%20was%20leading%20in%20just%20five%20of%20these%20seats%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20while%20the%20JMM-INC%20combine%20was%20dominant%20in%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Return%20Of%20Marandi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20bolstered%20by%20the%20return%20of%20former%20CM%20Babulal%20Marandi.%20His%20party%2C%20JVM(P)%2C%20won%20three%20seats%20with%20a%205.5%25%20vote%20share%20in%202019%20and%20harmed%20the%20BJP's%20chances%20in%20two%20seats%20during%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20Critics%2C%20however%2C%20argue%20that%20he%20is%20past%20his%20prime%20and%20point%20to%20the%20BJP's%20poor%20performance%20in%20ST-reserved%20seats%20during%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Sudesh%20Mahato's%20AJSU%2C%20which%20contested%20separately%20in%202019%20but%20has%20now%20rejoined%20the%20NDA%2C%20has%20a%20stronghold%20among%20Kurmi%20voters.%20The%20party%20won%20two%20seats%20with%20a%204.4%25%20vote%20share%20in%202019%20and%20adversely%20affected%20the%20BJP%20in%20three%20seats%2C%20receiving%20more%20votes%20than%20the%20winning%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAJSU%20may%20face%20competition%20from%20Jairam%20Mahato%2C%20a%20young%20Kurmi%20leader%20whose%20Jharkhand%20Bhasha%20Khatiyani%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%20(JBKSS)%20has%20been%20attracting%20large%20crowds.%20This%20party's%20main%20goal%20is%20to%20secure%20a%201932-based%20domicile%20policy%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20which%20deepens%20the%20insider-versus-outsider%20divide.%20In%20three%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20it%20aided%20the%20BJP%20by%20splitting%20the%20opposition%20vote%2C%20garnering%20between%209%25%20and%2027%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaryu%20Rai%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bgiant%20killer%26quot%3B%20who%20rebelled%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20defeated%20sitting%20CM%20Raghubar%20Das%2C%20has%20joined%20the%20JDU%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20allocated%20two%20seats.%20Rai%20enjoys%20a%20strong%20reputation%20in%20the%20Jamshedpur%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChampai's%20Entry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20strength%20has%20also%20increased%20with%20the%20entry%20of%20former%20CM%20Champai%20Soren%20from%20the%20JMM.%20Champai%20became%20CM%20when%20Hemant%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%20but%20was%20subsequently%20replaced%2C%20which%20hurt%20his%20pride%20and%20led%20him%20to%20join%20the%20BJP.%20He%20hails%20from%20the%20Kolhan%20region%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20single%20seat%20in%202019%2C%20while%20the%20JMM%20won%2013.%20The%20region%20has%2014%20seats%2C%20nine%20of%20which%20are%20reserved%20for%20the%20ST%20community.%20The%20Kurmi%20population%20there%20has%20turned%20against%20the%20JMM%20due%20to%20their%20exclusion%20from%20the%20ST%20list%2C%20which%20could%20benefit%20the%20BJP%2C%20particularly%20with%20Champai's%20involvement%2C%20though%20they%20must%20remain%20cautious%20of%20Jairam%20Mahto's%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20area%20for%20the%20BJP%20is%20Santhal%20Pargana%2C%20which%20has%2018%20seats%2C%20seven%20of%20which%20are%20reserved%20for%20the%20ST%20community.%20The%20BJP%20won%20only%20four%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20with%20the%20JMM%20claiming%2013.%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20emphasising%20the%20issue%20of%20infiltration%20in%20the%20region%2C%20which%20it%20claims%20is%20altering%20demographics.%20It%20hopes%20to%20leverage%20a%20tribal-versus-minorities%20narrative%20and%20has%20promised%20to%20implement%20the%20NRC%2C%20attempting%20to%20create%20a%20Hindutva%20narrative%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20regions%E2%80%94Kolhan%20and%20Santhal%20Pargana%E2%80%94comprising%2032%20seats%2C%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20BJP's%20comeback%20bid.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20only%20four%20of%20these%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20JMM%20secured%2026%2C%20giving%20them%20a%2022-seat%20advantage.%20If%20the%20BJP%20gains%20a%205%25%20vote%20share%20in%20these%20areas%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20JMM-INC%20alliance%2C%20it%20could%20potentially%20gain%20up%20to%2012%20seats%2C%20increasing%20its%20total%20to%2037%20and%20reducing%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%2035%2C%20placing%20them%20below%20the%20majority%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20INDIA%20Bloc%20Is%20Faring%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20strengthened%20with%20the%20inclusion%20of%20CPI-ML%20and%20CPIM%2C%20both%20of%20which%20have%20significant%20influence%20in%20the%20Palamu%20region%20bordering%20Bihar%20and%20around%20the%20Dhanbad%20coal%20belt.%20The%20MCC%2C%20another%20Left%20faction%2C%20merged%20with%20CPI-ML%20in%20August%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%202011%20census%2C%20the%20ST%20population%20in%20the%20state%20is%2026%25%2C%20while%20Christians%20make%20up%204%25.%20Tribal%20Christians%20dominate%20politics%2C%20particularly%20within%20the%20JMM.%20This%20has%20created%20social%20tension%2C%20as%20Sarna%20tribals%20believe%20that%20converted%20tribals%20are%20unjustly%20benefiting%20from%20reservations%20available%20to%20both%20minorities%20and%20STs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20exploiting%20this%20divide%20between%20Sarna%20and%20Tribal%20Christians.%20Most%20STs%20supporting%20the%20BJP%20are%20Sarna%20tribals.%20However%2C%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20garnered%20their%20support%20by%20promising%20to%20fulfil%20the%20long-standing%20demand%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Sarna%20Code%20and%20recognition%20as%20a%20separate%20religion%E2%80%94demands%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20historically%20opposed.%20This%20could%20complicate%20matters%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729256160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.co