country%20which%20jailed%20him%20for%20many%20years.%20Sinwar%20was%20named%20the%20group's%20paramount%20leader%20on%20August%206%2C%20as%20a%20successor%20to%20former%20political%20chief%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%2C%20who%20was%20assassinated%20in%20Tehran%20on%20July%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWidely%20known%20as%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Oct.%207%2C%202023%20attack%2C%20the%20most%20devastating%20event%20for%20Israel%20in%20decades%2C%20Sinwar%20has%20been%20in%20Gaza%2C%20defying%20Israeli%20attempts%20to%20kill%20him%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20a%20refugee%20camp%20in%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20city%20of%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20Sinwar%2C%2062%2C%20was%20elected%20as%20Hamas'%20leader%20in%20Gaza%20in%202017.%20The%20controversial%20leader%2C%20who%20spent%20half%20his%20adult%20life%20in%20Israeli%20prisons%2C%20was%20the%20most%20powerful%20Hamas%20leader%20left%20alive%20following%20the%20assassination%20of%20Haniyeh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWon't%20Release%20Hostages%3A%20Hamas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20today%20said%20it%20won't%20release%20hostages%20until%20Israel%20ends%20its%20war%20on%20Gaza%2C%20withdraws%20from%20the%20territory%20and%20frees%20jailed%20Palestinians.%20The%20hostages%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20return...%20unless%20the%20aggression%20against%20our%20people%20in%20Gaza%20stops%2C%20there%20is%20a%20complete%20withdrawal%20from%20it%2C%20and%20our%20heroic%20prisoners%20are%20released%20from%20the%20occupation's%20prisons%2C%26quot%3B%20Khalil%20al-Haya%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Reuters%20and%20AFP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729255980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fnqrfg8sg_yahya-sinwar_650x400_17_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-confirms-yahya-sinwar-killed-by-israel-wo