tricacies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20prelims%20comprise%20two%20sections%20of%20General%20Studies%20and%20CSAT.%20The%20latter%20is%20a%20qualifying%20paper%20where%20about%2080%20questions%20are%20asked.%20To%20clear%20the%20exam%2C%20one%20needs%20approximately%2068%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%20200%20marks.%20In%20my%20first%20attempt%2C%20although%20I%20scored%20well%20in%20General%20Studies%2C%20I%20failed%20in%20CSAT%20by%20just%20three%20marks.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20the%20gap%20increased%20to%20nine%20marks%20when%20I%20reappeared%20for%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20middle-income%20background%2C%20Karamveer%20also%20faced%20immense%20pressure%20at%20home.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20and%20our%20family%20was%20surviving%20on%20his%20monthly%20pension.%20There%20is%20immense%20uncertainty%20in%20this%20exam%2C%20and%20having%20failed%20twice%20added%20to%20the%20pressure.%20My%20family%20was%20confused%20about%20why%20I%20could%20not%20even%20clear%20the%20prelims.%20It%20was%20becoming%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20stay%20motivated%20given%20the%20circumstances%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karamveer%20suggests%20analysing%20the%20last%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20and%20their%20answer%20keys%20to%20improve%20marks%20in%20CSAT.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558-500x262.jpg%20500w