rcome%20the%20challenges%20presented%20by%20this%20crucial%20component%20of%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362685%2Fhow-to-clear-upsc-cse-from-home-irms-officer-akash-chavda-prep-journey-delhi-coaching-busting-myths%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20UPSC%20examination%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Karamveer%20strategically%20adjusted%20his%20preparation%20approach.%20He%20dedicated%20about%20three%20hours%20of%20study%20each%20day%20for%20three%20months%20to%20excel%20in%20this%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20merely%20attempting%20more%20comprehension%20questions%20was%20not%20enough.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20times%2C%20questions%20on%20basics%20like%20permutations%20and%20combinations%2C%20profit%20and%20loss%2C%20and%20percentages%20are%20designed%20to%20challenge%20even%20IIT%20students.%20To%20ace%20both%20Maths%20and%20Logical%20Reasoning%2C%20I%20started%20referring%20to%20notes%20meant%20for%20the%20CAT%20(Common%20Admission%20Test)%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaramveer%20also%20began%20analysing%20the%20last%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20and%20their%20answer%20keys.%20This%20analysis%20helped%20him%20understand%20the%20type%20of%20questions%20to%20expect%20in%20the%20exam.%20By%20focusing%20on%20all%20three%20sections%20of%20the%20CSAT%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20questions%20he%20attempted.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20says%2C%20he%20could%20score%2090%20out%20of%20the%20200%20marks%20in%20the%20exam%20on%20his%20third%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaramveer%20highlights%20the%20significance%20of%20perseverance%2C%20adaptability%2C%20and%20strategic%20planning%20in%20overcoming%20challenges%20and%20achieving%20one%E2%80%99s%20goals.%20His%20journey%20underscores%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20well-rounded%20preparation%20strategy%20that%20encompasses%20not%20only%20a%20strong%20grasp%20of%20the%20subject